inen","twined","woven","work","with","cherubs"]},{"verseId":"brenton_exodus_37_6","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":2,"bookName":"Exodus","bookAbbrev":"exodus","chapter":37,"verse":6,"text":"and their posts five, and the rings; and they gilded their chapiters and their clasps with gold, and they had five sockets of brass.","searchKeywords":["and","their","posts","five","the","rings","they","gilded","chapiters","clasps","with","gold","had","sockets","brass"]},{"verseId":"brenton_exodus_37_7","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":2,"bookName":"Exodus","bookAbbrev":"exodus","chapter":37,"verse":7,"text":"And they made the court toward the south; the curtains of the court of fine linen twined, a hundred every way,","searchKeywords":["and","they","made","the","court","toward","south","curtains","fine","linen","twined","hundred","every","way"]},{"verseId":"brenton_exodus_37_8","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":2,"bookName":"Exodus","bookAbbrev":"exodus","chapter":37,"verse":8,"text":"and their posts twenty, and their sockets twenty;","searchKeywords":["and","their","posts","twenty","sockets"]},{"verseId":"brenton_exodus_37_9","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":2,"bookName":"Exodus","bookAbbrev":"exodus","chapter":37,"verse":9,"text":"and on the north side a hundred every way, and on the south side a hundred every way, and their posts twenty and their sockets twenty.","searchKeywords":["and","the","north","side","hundred","every","way","south","their","posts","twenty","sockets"]},{"verseId":"brenton_exodus_37_10","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":2,"bookName":"Exodus","bookAbbrev":"exodus","chapter":37,"verse":10,"text":"And on the west side curtains of fifty cubits, their posts ten and their sockets ten.","searchKeywords":["and","the","west","side","curtains","fifty","cubits","their","posts","ten","sockets"]},{"verseId":"brenton_exodus_37_11","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":2,"bookName":"Exodus","bookAbbrev":"exodus","chapter":37,"verse":11,"text":"And on the east side curtains of fifty cubits of fifteen cubits behind,","searchKeywords":["and","the","east","side","curtains","fifty","cubits","fifteen","behind"]},{"verseId":"brenton_exodus_37_12","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":2,"bookName":"Exodus","bookAbbrev":"exodus","chapter":37,"verse":12,"text":"and their pillars three, and their sockets three.","searchKeywords":["and","their","pillars","three","sockets"]},{"verseId":"brenton_exodus_37_13","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":2,"bookName":"Exodus","bookAbbrev":"exodus","chapter":37,"verse":13,"text":"And at the second back on this side and on that by the gate of the court, curtains of fifteen cubits, their pillars three and their sockets three;","searchKeywords":["and","the","second","back","this","side","that","gate","court","curtains","fifteen","cubits","their","pillars","three","sockets"]},{"verseId":"brenton_exodus_37_14","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":2,"bookName":"Exodus","bookAbbrev":"exodus","chapter":37,"verse":14,"text":"all the curtains of the tabernacle of fine linen twined.","searchKeywords":["all","the","curtains","tabernacle","fine","linen","twined"]},{"verseId":"brenton_exodus_37_15","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":2,"bookName":"Exodus","bookAbbrev":"exodus","chapter":37,"verse":15,"text":"And the sockets of their pillars of brass, and their hooks of silver, and their chapiters overlaid with silver, and all the posts of the court overlaid with silver:","searchKeywords":["and","the","sockets","their","pillars","brass","hooks","silver","chapiters","overlaid","with","all","posts","court"]},{"verseId":"brenton_exodus_37_16","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":2,"bookName":"Exodus","bookAbbrev":"exodus","chapter":37,"verse":16,"text":"and the veil of the gate of the court, the work of an emb